# CourtSlot index — daily maintenance
#
# Install (pick one):
#
#   crontab -e
#   # paste the line below (adjust BACKEND path and optionally python/venv)
#
# Or install this file:
#   crontab api-services/backend/scripts/cron/crontab.example
#
# Every day at 01:00 UTC — prune past slots and extend the horizon (default 60 days)
0 1 * * * /Users/admin-2/Desktop/personal/django-react/api-services/backend/scripts/cron/generate_court_slots.sh

# Optional: extend horizon to 1 year (pass --days to the management command)
# 0 1 * * * /path/to/api-services/backend/scripts/cron/generate_court_slots.sh --days 365

# Logs: api-services/backend/logs/generate_court_slots.log
